episodes.title: Bondi Hearing Leaves Unanswered Questions About Epstein
episodes.description:
Democrats want more answers after Attorney General Pam Bondi testified for hours about files related to files disgraced financier Jeffrey Epstein. Tyler Kendall reports.

episodes.title: Pam Bondi Doesn't Care About Epstein Victims: Ty Cobb
episodes.description:
Ty Cobb, former Special Counsel to President Trump during the First Administration, reacts to US Attorney General Pam Bondi's testimony on Capitol Hill stating she's reprehensible and covering up for perpetrators in the Epstein Files. He also calls for the resignation of Secretary of Commerce Howard Lutnick following Lutnick's testimony on Capitol Hill, and gives his response to a direct callout from President Trump on the president's social media platform. Ty Cobb speaks with Kailey Leinz and Joe Mathieu on the late edition of Bloomberg's "Balance of Power."
